<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>500 - Internal Server Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #c0392b;
            max-width: 80%;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #3498db;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Oops! 500</h1>
    <p>Something went wrong on our end.</p>
    <p class="error-message"><%= errorMessage %></p>
    <p>Don't worry, we're on it. Meanwhile, you can:</p>
    <a href="/">Go to Home</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
